('S0385', 'T1056', '.001', '[njRAT](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0385) is capable of logging keystrokes.(Citation: Fidelis njRAT June 2013)(Citation: Trend Micro njRAT 2018)(Citation: Citizen Lab Group5)'),
('S0385', 'T1112', '', '[njRAT](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0385) can create, delete, or modify a specified Registry key or value.(Citation: Fidelis njRAT June 2013)(Citation: Trend Micro njRAT 2018)'),
