('S0111', 'T1053', '.005', '[schtasks](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0111) is used to schedule tasks on a Windows system to run at a specific date and time.(Citation: TechNet Schtasks)'),
('S0227', 'T1213', '.002', '[spwebmember](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0227) is used to enumerate and dump information from Microsoft SharePoint.(Citation: NCC Group APT15 Alive and Strong)'),
('S0225', 'T1190', '', '[sqlmap](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0225) can be used to automate exploitation of SQL injection vulnerabilities.(Citation: sqlmap Introduction)'),
('S0123', 'T1569', '.002', '[xCmd](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0123) can be used to execute binaries on remote systems by creating and starting a service.(Citation: xCmd)'),
('S0248', 'T1102', '.002', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) communicates to the C2 server by retrieving a Google Doc.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1027', '.001', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) contains junk code in its binary, likely to confuse malware analysts.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1005', '', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) collects files with the following extensions: .ppt, .pptx, .pdf, .doc, .docx, .xls, .xlsx, .docm, .rtf, .inp, .xlsm, .csv, .odt, .pps, .vcf and sends them back to the C2 server.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1083', '', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) gathers information on victim’s drives and has a plugin for document listing.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1056', '.001', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) uses a keylogger plugin to gather keystrokes.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1057', '', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) gets an output of running processes using the <code>tasklist</code> command.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1018', '', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) uses the <code>net view</code> command for discovery.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1053', '.005', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) establishes persistence by creating a scheduled task with the command <code>SchTasks /Create /SC DAILY /TN BigData /TR “ + path_file + “/ST 09:30“</code>.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1113', '', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) collects screenshots of the victim machine.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1027', '.002', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) packs a plugin with UPX.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1497', '.001', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) has some basic anti-sandbox detection that tries to detect Virtual PC, Sandboxie, and VMware. (Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1082', '', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) gathers the computer name, the serial number of the main disk volume, CPU information, Microsoft Windows version, and runs the command <code>systeminfo</code>.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1016', '', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) runs <code>ipconfig /all</code> and collects the domain name.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0248', 'T1033', '', '[yty](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0248) collects the victim’s username.(Citation: ASERT Donot March 2018)'),
('S0350', 'T1070', '.004', '[zwShell](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0350) has deleted itself after creating a service as well as deleted a temporary file when the system reboots.(Citation: McAfee Night Dragon)'),
('S0350', 'T1083', '', '[zwShell](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0350) can browse the file system.(Citation: McAfee Night Dragon)'),
